			&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;First thing to know about using the forums is that they are not hosted on this site, so, your member username and password won't work to log in with their site.  Here's what you need to do in order to sign up for a username from EZBoard:
<ol type="1">
<li>Click on the Forum link to open the forums in a new window.<br>
<li>Click on the link on the forum page on the third text line down on the left.  It says Register Your Free Account (Required).
<li>If you want to be able to use this username to post in any EZBoard forum then sign up for a Global Account, otherwise if you're sure you'll only be using it in the Epic Shadows forum OR someone has already taken that username Globally, create a Local account.
