<li>It will take you to your own personal control center where you can either create a forum or just link to other forums.  There should be a list on that page of your recently visisted forums with Epic Shadows in it.  Click on that link to go to the forum.
<li>Next time you come to the forums if you are not logged in with your username just click on the login link on the same line as the link that you used to create your account.
</ol>

