<li>If you come up with a fun or fancy title that you want to show up when you post, let me know and I might put it in :)
<li>USE THEM!  These forums are very helpful, yet we still have a marginal percentage of the guild actively participating in them.  They help me and everyone else know what you want to accomplish and also gives us an opportunity to talk about stuff before we run out and do it.
